Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:12.45,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Ogata here! What was that slide just now?!\N Is something wrong, Kanata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.11,Default,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax-0.2\t(976,977,\fax0)\move(325,342,320,342,976,977)}Are you having issues\N with the car's balance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.12,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,No problems. Just a minor adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.66,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,The Honda and Alfa in front \Nof me are battling hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.62,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,But with no one around me, \NI can take my ideal lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:29.26,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,And the moment where \NI join their battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.29,Default,Kanata,0000,0000,0000,,may come sooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:37.89,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,Join that dogfight?\NI wonder how serious he is about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:42.41,Italics,Ogata,0000,0000,0000,,when there's such a huge gulf between \Nhis car's power and everyone else's.
