Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.96,Default,MFG Staff,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a change of positions,\N so whenever you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.12,Default,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:25.39,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something, Kyoko-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:30.35,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, ask me anything. \NAfter all, it is your first race, Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.65,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:37.36,Default,Leaderboard signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs28\fscx85\c&H40372E&\pos(358.667,62)}Yashio Kakeru
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.36,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they using an analog leaderboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.23,Default,Leaderboard signs,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fs28\fscx85\c&H40372E&\pos(363.333,164.667)}Kitahara Nozomi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.32,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Everything else in MFG is so high tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:44.79,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a sharp eye. \NWell, just watch and it'll all become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.75,Default,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:53.46,Default,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't zoom in on my butt, Uehara-san.\N I'm {\i1}super{\i0} self-conscious about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.21,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.42,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Fanservice is an important part of this gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:03.82,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel Cam is popular\Nand gets a ton of views.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.22,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Better brace yourself for it, Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.92,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.20,Default,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,And now, it's Question Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:13.95,Top Italics,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,Moe-chan, who's your favorite driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.65,Top Italics,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's such a hard question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:23.62,Default,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,All the drivers are wonderful, \Nbut kind of hard to approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:28.08,Default,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,They're a little too intimidating for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.60,Top Italics,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,So my favorite is all 15 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:35.73,Top Italics,Moe,0000,0000,0000,,And as long as everyone makes it across\N the line safely, I'll be super happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.80,Top Italics,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,What a perfect answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.86,Default,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute, Moe-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.26,Top Italics,Staff,0000,0000,0000,,That was the fans' number one, Moe-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.45,Italics,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a corny act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:48.73,Italics,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,If there were a vote on who has the worst \Npersonality, you'd be number one with a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:52.12,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this job was \Nmostly singing and dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.81,Italics,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,Being an Angel is tougher than I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:07.65,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the second half now. Just a little \Nbit further and the course goes uphill again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:11.92,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna need to put some distance between us\Nand the 86 to give us a decent margin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:15.88,Italics,Kakeru,0000,0000,0000,,Because when we get to Sector 3,\Nhe'll gain a lot of speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:21.38,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And the two leaders are through the \NTorii gate, with Beckenbauer on the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.43,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,He's got Ishigami by the tail \Nand isn't letting go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:30.18,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,This must be hard for Ishigami-kun. \NI don't think he's got much breathing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:35.85,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,As reigning champ two years running, I'd like \Nto see him stand up to this rising star, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.81,Italics,Ishigami,0000,0000,0000,,How damn embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:43.78,Italics,Ishigami,0000,0000,0000,,A standard Cayman managing\Nto chase down the famous GT3...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.49,Italics,Ishigami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it getting under my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:52.07,Italics,Ishigami,0000,0000,0000,,Is the fact that he graduated from the \NPorsche Academy making me self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:13:00.73,Italics,Ishigami,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I shake the feeling that \NI'm being looked down upon from up high?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:08.64,Default,Michael,0000,0000,0000,,Do you deserve to be \Ndriving that car, Ishigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:13.97,Italics,Michael,0000,0000,0000,,The 991 GT3 is the ultimate \Nin Porsche rear-engine models.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:18.78,Italics,Michael,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know how to drive it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.48,Italics,Michael,0000,0000,0000,,Does a street monkey \Nfrom the far reaches of Asia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:27.24,Italics,Michael,0000,0000,0000,,even have the right to sit in \Nthe seat of a German masterpiece?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.80,Italics,Michael,0000,0000,0000,,Prove it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.58,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And here's the battle for third,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.36,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,arguably the most hotly \Ncontested position in the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:50.74,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,You can see Aiba Shun ducking left and right,\Ntrying to chase down Sakamoto in the 5 car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:54.43,Default,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way, you dark side shadow lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.78,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,How dumb can you get? \NAre you even thinking about your tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.50,Italics,Sakamoto,0000,0000,0000,,And having to put up \Nwith it is stressing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:05.19,Italics,Aiba,0000,0000,0000,,Number Seven's kiss belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.12,Default,Kyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:10.93,Default,Seven,0000,0000,0000,,I just got these weird chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.61,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Akaba in the 2 car has taken off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:18.19,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,He glides past Natsume's \NBMW and takes ninth place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.75,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,In qualifying, a turbo issue \Ncost him a few places,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:25.48,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,but Akaba-kun isn't the kind of driver \Nwho's satisfied with that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:31.06,Top Italics,Kogashiwa,0000,0000,0000,,He was second last year, and as a \Nracing driver, he's a first-class talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:39.75,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, Akaba has the Lamborghini\N in front in his crosshairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.66,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Akaba Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.65,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.22,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,Swelled up on all that turbo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.91,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,That prancing horse badge\Ndoesn't mean what it used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:15:00.58,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear my naturally aspirated \N5.2 liter engine chuckling behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:05.50,Italics,Akaba,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel particularly \Nattached to the Ferrari brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:10.75,Italics,Akaba,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a superior weapon in fights\N like these, so I make use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:17.55,Italics,Akaba,0000,0000,0000,,So why is it I find that bull \Nemblem so damn annoying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:22.57,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,Lambos are the real kings \Nof the supercar these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.61,Italics,Oishi,0000,0000,0000,,And your grand prix \Nlineage can kiss my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:31.57,Italics,Akaba,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear a whispering in my ear:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:34.12,Italics,Akaba,0000,0000,0000,,"Let him have it. Onwards."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.26,Italics,Akaba,0000,0000,0000,,"This is one car's dust \Nyou mustn't get left in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:43.83,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,And the leaders pass by \Nthe highest point on Route 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.71,Top Italics,Commentator,0000,0000,0000,,The two Porsches blaze into Sector 3.
